   Drug Abuse Prevention Research meeting.. details in text 2^nd National
   Conference on Drug Abuse Prevention Research:
   A Progress Update
   This Conference was held at the Omni Shoreham Hotel in Washington D.C.,
   August 9-10, 2001.
